                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " These reactions",
                "were used to calculate the flux of bremsstrahlung",
                "gamma-quanta. For this, a rectangular natural lutetium",
                "target 1 x 0.7 x 0.007 cm in size and about 0.05 g in",
                "weight was placed in an aluminum cylinder together with",
                "the studied samples."
              ]
            }
          ],
